    "description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you cast an </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>instantaneous </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">spell, if you have an </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>arcane </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">weapon equipped, you may </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>increase the spell's total MP cost</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">by up to </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>【</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>SL × 10</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><strong>】 </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Mind Points. If you do so and the spell deals damage to one or more creatures, it will deal 5 extra damage to each creature for every 10 Mind Points by which you increased its total MP cost.</span> </p><hr /><p>Skill Level <strong>1</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[10 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>2</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[20 mp]</strong></p><p>Skill Level <strong>3</strong> - <strong>@LOSS[30 mp]</strong></p>",
